adhoc_settings.description:
Ad-hoc settings to override update workflow configuration for huge projects. See <a href="https://botify.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/ENG/pages/3789684780/Log+Analyzer+for+big+clients+Playbook+BLA">doc</a> for details.<br>ex:<br><pre>{
  "merge_urls_group_chunk_size": 2,
  "seen_chain_chunk_size": 12,
  "history_seen_chain_chunk_size": 6,
  "make_hashes_files_group_chunk_size": 4
}</pre>
